# Force LF line endings for files that are read as text resources or templates.
# Keeps embedded SKILL.md and other text artifacts byte-identical across platforms,
# so binary contents (and tests asserting on `\n`) remain stable on Windows CI.
.claude/skills/yt/SKILL.md text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.cs text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf
*.yml text eol=lf
*.toml text eol=lf
